{"tid":548921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擲千萬買樓盼子入喇沙 重慶母否認分薄港學位","createTime":"2018-02-03T06:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T14:42:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1d251de16092b3ece194600f2df592c0dcd5e949","tid":548921,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180203/large/1517625096_b544.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180203%2Flarge%2F1517625096_b544.png&h=fb657425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小一入學統一派位今日開始報名，在九龍城41名校網，不少家長冒著嚴寒，在早上8時許到達派位中心交表。龍年效應下、學額競爭激烈，有內地的家長提早幾年籌謀子女來港升學，來自重慶的汪太今早為兒子報名，她表示，第一志願為名校喇沙小學，早於2014年已斥資逾1,300萬元來九龍城校網置業。<br />\n<br />\n為備戰升小，她為兒子報讀不少興趣班，如學術、藝術及體育，現在正學習跆拳道及游泳等，她去年已為兒子報讀10多間香港私立及直資小學，目前已獲7間取錄。但她表示仍以喇沙為第一志願，如無法入讀心儀的喇沙，才會考慮就讀該等直資或私立學校。<br />\n<br />\n對於有香港家長認為，內地學生或分薄學位，汪太指「不能這樣說」，認為教育的競爭並非內地與香港人爭，而是全球化競爭，香港家長不應該認為內地人來搶學位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180203/57787456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57787456&d=uX%2BhsQGbvnpEibZKVEWEKcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2ffd6d7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57787456&h=335856e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180203/57787456</a>"},{"pid":"a3f16201dfe4759c1d005cd7228f074e83684b48","tid":548921,"uid":55488,"like":14,"dislike":14,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:18:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"068fdb546dc8515b6c2f870076ec8bc04b6ff0f1","tid":548921,"uid":8867,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93214a3c7c5e8245d283bc3060e12316a5f367ea","tid":548921,"uid":85163,"like":10,"dislike":1